case.title: Looking for a relationship - 29 (London)
case.text: Are there any genuine single attractive guys out there who are looking for a relationship and NOT a hook up? I'm an attractive south asian girl who has a preference for white men and I am 100% genuine. Please reply with a picture and the word "bingo" in the subject heading so I know you have read my message. You must provide at least 2 pictures to get a response.
